## üóÇÔ∏è **Basic Linux Commands**

| Command   | Description                        |
| --------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `pwd`     | Present working directory kaatuvum |
| `ls`      | Files list panna                   |
| `cd`      | Directory change panna             |
| `mkdir`   | New directory create panna         |
| `rmdir`   | Empty directory remove panna       |
| `rm`      | File or folder remove panna        |
| `cp`      | Copy files or folders              |
| `mv`      | Move or rename file                |
| `touch`   | Empty file create panna            |
| `cat`     | File content display panna         |
| `head`    | File oda first 10 lines kaatuvum   |
| `tail`    | File oda last 10 lines kaatuvum    |
| `clear`   | Screen clear panna                 |
| `history` | Command history kaatuvum           |

