## üìÅ **File Permissions and Ownership**

| Command | Description                       |
| ------- | --------------------------------- |
| `chmod` | File permission change panna      |
| `chown` | File owner change panna           |
| `chgrp` | Group ownership change panna      |
| `umask` | Default permission mask set panna |

