## ‚öôÔ∏è **System Information**

| Command    | Description                |
| ---------- | -------------------------- |
| `uname -a` | System info kaatuvum       |
| `hostname` | System name kaatuvum       |
| `uptime`   | System running time        |
| `date`     | Current date and time      |
| `cal`      | Calendar kaatuvum          |
| `df -h`    | Disk space usage           |
| `du -sh *` | Folder size list           |
| `top`      | Running process list live  |
| `htop`     | Advanced top (interactive) |
| `free -h`  | Memory usage               |
| `whoami`   | Current user name          |
| `id`       | User ID and group info     |

