## üîÑ **Compression and Archive**

| Command                     | Description                 |
| --------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| `tar -cvf file.tar folder/` | Folder archive create panna |
| `tar -xvf file.tar`         | Extract panna               |
| `gzip file`                 | Compress panna              |
| `gunzip file.gz`            | Decompress panna            |
| `zip -r file.zip folder/`   | Zip file create panna       |
| `unzip file.zip`            | Extract zip file            |

