## üîê **File Permission Numbers**

| Number | Meaning |
| ------ | ------- |
| 0      | ---     |
| 1      | --x     |
| 2      | -w-     |
| 3      | -wx     |
| 4      | r--     |
| 5      | r-x     |
| 6      | rw-     |
| 7      | rwx     |

Example ‚Üí `chmod 755 file`

