| `reboot`                  | System restart         |
| `shutdown -h now`         | Shutdown immediately   |
| `service <name> start`    | Start service          |
| `service <name> stop`     | Stop service           |
| `systemctl status <name>` | Check service status   |
| `journalctl -xe`          | System logs view panna |

